              <li><span class="check-icon">‚úì</span> Kitchen appliances</li>
              <li><span class="check-icon">‚úì</span> High-resolution photos</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-column">
            <h5>PDF Report</h5>
            <ul>
              <li><span class="check-icon">‚úì</span> AI-assisted issue analysis</li>
              <li><span class="check-icon">‚úì</span> Severity classification</li>
              <li><span class="check-icon">‚úì</span> Photo evidence included</li>
              <li><span class="check-icon">‚úì</span> 24-hour delivery</li>
              <li><span class="check-icon">‚úì</span> Timestamped records</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Value Comparison -->
  <div class="value-comparison">
    <h3 class="comparison-title">The Real Cost of Skipping Documentation Visits</h3>

    <div class="comparison-grid">
      <div class="comparison-item">
        <div class="comparison-icon cost-icon">üí∏</div>
        <div class="comparison-value">$5,000+</div>
        <div class="comparison-label">Average Major Repair</div>
        <p class="comparison-description">Water damage, HVAC replacement, or structural issues</p>
      </div>

      <div class="comparison-item">
        <div class="comparison-icon cost-icon">‚è±Ô∏è</div>
        <div class="comparison-value">2-4 weeks</div>
        <div class="comparison-label">Emergency Repair Time</div>
        <p class="comparison-description">Tenant displacement and lost rental income</p>
      </div>

      <div class="comparison-item highlight">
        <div class="comparison-icon save-icon">‚ú®</div>
        <div class="comparison-value">$400/year</div>
        <div class="comparison-label">Quarterly Documentation Visits</div>
        <p class="comparison-description">Catch issues early, avoid expensive surprises</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="roi-message">
      <div class="roi-icon">üí°</div>
      <p><strong>Just one prevented repair pays for an entire year</strong> ‚Äî Plus you get peace of mind, tenant satisfaction, and detailed property records.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .pricing-section {
    padding: 8rem 3rem;
    max-width: 1400px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    position: relative;
  }

  .pricing-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .section-eyebrow {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  body.light-mode .section-eyebrow {
    color: #666666;
  }

  .pricing-header h2 {
    font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffffff 0%, #94a3b8 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  }

  body.light-mode .pricing-header h2 {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a1a 0%, #333333 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  }

  .section-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  body.light-mode .section-subtitle {
    color: #4a4a4a;
  }

  /* Pricing Card */
  .pricing-card-container {
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto 5rem;
  }

  .pricing-card {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg,
      rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05) 0%,
      rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02) 100%);
    border: 2px solid rgba(231, 76, 60, 0.3);
    border-radius: 32px;
    padding: 3rem;
    position: relative;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    transition: all 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
  }

  .pricing-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-8px);
    border-color: rgba(231, 76, 60, 0.5);
    box-shadow: 0 30px 80px rgba(231, 76, 60, 0.25);
  }

  body.light-mode .pricing-card {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
    border-color: rgba(231, 76, 60, 0.3);
  }

  .pricing-badge {
    position: absolute;
    top: -15px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e74c3c 0%, #c0392b 100%);
    color: white;
    padding: 0.5rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(231, 76, 60, 0.4);
  }

  .plan-name {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  body.light-mode .plan-name {
    color: #1a1a1a;
  }

  .plan-description {
    text-align: center;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  body.light-mode .plan-description {
    color: #666666;
  }

  .price-display {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .price-currency {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    vertical-align: top;
    margin-right: 0.25rem;
  }

  .price-amount {
    font-size: 4.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e74c3c 0%, #ff6b6b 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .price-period {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  body.light-mode .price-currency {
    color: #1a1a1a;
  }

  body.light-mode .price-period {
    color: #666666;
  }

  .price-breakdown {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .price-breakdown p {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  body.light-mode .price-breakdown p {
    color: #888888;
  }

  .plan-cta {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    padding: 1.2rem 2rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e74c3c 0%, #c0392b 100%);
    color: white;
    text-align: center;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 16px;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
    box-shadow: 0 6px 25px rgba(231, 76, 60, 0.35);
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .plan-cta:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 35px rgba(231, 76, 60, 0.45);
  }

  .plan-features h4 {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  body.light-mode .plan-features h4 {
    color: #1a1a1a;
  }

  .features-columns {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .feature-column h5 {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #e74c3c;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(231, 76, 60, 0.3);
  }

  .plan-features ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .plan-features li {
    padding: 0.5rem 0;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  body.light-mode .plan-features li {
    color: #4a4a4a;
  }

  .check-icon {
    color: #10b981;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 500px) {
    .features-columns {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }
  }

  /* Value Comparison */
  .value-comparison {
    margin-bottom: 5rem;
  }

  .comparison-title {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffffff 0%, #94a3b8 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  }

  body.light-mode .comparison-title {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a1a 0%, #333333 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  }

  .comparison-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .comparison-item {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    text-align: center;
    transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
  }

  .comparison-item.highlight {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg,
      rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.1) 0%,
      rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.05) 100%);
    border-color: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.3);
  }

  .comparison-item:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
  }

  body.light-mode .comparison-item {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
    border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
  }

  body.light-mode .comparison-item.highlight {
    background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.08);
    border-color: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.2);
  }

  .comparison-icon {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .comparison-value {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .cost-icon + .comparison-value {
    color: #ef4444;
  }

  .save-icon + .comparison-value {
    color: #10b981;
  }

  body.light-mode .cost-icon + .comparison-value {
    color: #dc2626;
  }

  body.light-mode .save-icon + .comparison-value {
    color: #059669;
  }

  .comparison-label {
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  body.light-mode .comparison-label {
    color: #1a1a1a;
  }

  .comparison-description {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  body.light-mode .comparison-description {
    color: #666666;
  }

  .roi-message {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    padding: 2rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg,
      rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.1) 0%,
      rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.05) 100%);
    border: 1px solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.3);
    border-radius: 20px;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  body.light-mode .roi-message {
    background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.08);
  }

  .roi-icon {
    font-size: 3rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .roi-message p {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0;
  }

  body.light-mode .roi-message p {
    color: #1a1a1a;
  }

  .roi-message strong {
    color: rgb(59, 130, 246);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .pricing-section {
      padding: 4rem 1.5rem;
    }

    .pricing-card {
      padding: 2rem;
    }

    .comparison-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .roi-message {
      flex-direction: column;
      text-align: center;
    }
  }
</style>
